                            <comment id="12704276" author="nk11" created="Wed, 29 Apr 2009 19:30:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It doesn&apos;t work yet.&lt;br/&gt;
In the StorageService.setup() there still is a Token.toString:&lt;br/&gt;
new ApplicationState(storageMetadata_.getStorageId().toString())&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12704279" author="jbellis" created="Wed, 29 Apr 2009 19:39:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;you&apos;re right.  updated patch attached.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12704679" author="nk11" created="Thu, 30 Apr 2009 16:04:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the last one did it &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
