                            <comment id="12704980" author="hudson" created="Fri, 1 May 2009 13:09:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra #55 (See &lt;a href=&quot;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/55/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/55/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
